      <title>拉脱维亚总统称俄罗斯无人机在北约成员国拉脱维亚坠毁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/russian-drone-crashes-in-nato-member-latvia-its-president-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，在乌克兰遭遇的另一场无人机连环袭击中，拉脱维亚和罗马尼亚分别报告了涉及俄罗斯无人机的事件，这表明该地区国家面临的空中威胁日益增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/russian-drone-crashes-in-nato-member-latvia-its-president-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 13:48:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾逮捕杜特尔特牧师，与马科斯矛盾加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/philippines-arrests-duterte-s-pastor-ally-wanted-by-fbi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦调查局通缉的一名福音派传教士被捕，此人与前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特及其家人关系密切，而该家族与总统费迪南德·马科斯之间的裂痕正在加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/philippines-arrests-duterte-s-pastor-ally-wanted-by-fbi</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 11:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰在委内瑞拉反对派领导人逃亡前为其提供庇护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/netherlands-sheltered-venezuela-opposition-leader-before-he-fled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派候选人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯（Edmundo González）于周日逃往西班牙，在此之前，荷兰曾在加拉加斯的荷兰大使馆秘密庇护了他六周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/netherlands-sheltered-venezuela-opposition-leader-before-he-fled</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 10:49:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约时报-锡耶纳学院全国民意调查显示特朗普领先哈里斯一个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/trump-leads-harris-by-a-point-in-nyt-siena-college-national-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国大选进入最后阶段，共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普在《纽约时报》和锡耶纳学院进行的一项最新全国民意调查中领先副总统卡马拉·哈里斯一个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/trump-leads-harris-by-a-point-in-nyt-siena-college-national-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 10:17:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国的斯塔默警告称，极右翼提供“骗人的”简单答案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/uk-s-starmer-warns-far-right-offers-snake-oil-of-easy-answers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，他希望通过对经济进行根本性改革来对抗英国极右翼势力的崛起，尽管这一过程中必须做出不受欢迎的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/uk-s-starmer-warns-far-right-offers-snake-oil-of-easy-answers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 09:53:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>战争持续，苏丹军队拒绝联合国派遣维和部队的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/sudan-s-army-rejects-un-proposal-of-peacekeepers-as-war-rages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏丹军方领导的政府拒绝了联合国实况调查团提出的向这个被 17 个月的内战所困扰的北非国家派遣一支独立维和部队的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/sudan-s-army-rejects-un-proposal-of-peacekeepers-as-war-rages</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 09:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
